import React from "react"; import parse from "html-react-parser"; const WhatWeOfferSix = ({ tagline, title, backfont, text, textBtn, pathBtn, data, }) => (

{tagline}

{title && parse(title)}

{text && parse(text)}

{textBtn || "Read more"}

{data.map((service, i) => (
{service.title}
{service.text}
))}
); export default WhatWeOfferSix;
